---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Terms of Service, edgepush" description="edgepush terms of service. Usage rules, uptime expectations, and open source licensing.">
  <main class="flex-1 font-sans">
    <nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1440px] items-center justify-between border-b border-rule px-6 py-5">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="flex items-center gap-2.5 font-mono text-[15px] font-bold text-text"
      >
        <span class="relative flex h-[22px] w-[22px] items-center justify-center border border-accent font-mono text-[11px] font-extrabold text-accent">
          ep
        </span>
        edgepush
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.1em]">
        <a
          href="https://app.edgepush.dev/sign-in"
          class="rounded-none border border-rule-strong px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-text hover:border-text"
        >
          sign_in
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <article class="mx-auto max-w-[780px] px-6 py-16">
      <div class="mb-3 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-muted">
        <span class="text-accent">─&nbsp;</span> legal / terms
      </div>
      <h1 class="mb-2 font-mono text-[40px] font-extrabold leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.03em] text-text">
        terms of service.
      </h1>
      <p class="mb-14 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-muted">
        last updated: 2026-04-10
      </p>

      <!-- acceptance -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-[18px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-text">
          <span class="text-accent">├&nbsp;</span>
          acceptance
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-muted-strong">
          By using the hosted edgepush service, you agree to these terms. If
          you do not agree, do not use the service.
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- the service -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-[18px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-text">
          <span class="text-accent">├&nbsp;</span>
          the service
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-muted-strong">
          edgepush is an open source push notification relay. The hosted
          version is provided free of charge as a convenience for users who do
          not want to self-host. No SLA is offered.
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- your responsibilities -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-[18px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-text">
          <span class="text-accent">├&nbsp;</span>
          your responsibilities
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-muted-strong">
          <ul class="list-none space-y-3">
            <li>
              <span class="text-accent">● </span>
              You are responsible for keeping your account credentials secure.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-accent">● </span>
              You must not send spam, phishing, or any unsolicited or deceptive
              messages to end users.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-accent">● </span>
              You must comply with Apple APNs and Google FCM terms of service
              when sending messages through their networks.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-accent">● </span>
              You must not attempt to reverse-engineer, abuse, or overload the
              service.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-accent">● </span>
              You are responsible for obtaining consent from end users before
              sending them push notifications where required by law.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- open source -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-[18px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-text">
          <span class="text-accent">├&nbsp;</span>
          open source
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-muted-strong">
          edgepush is dual-licensed. The server and dashboard are AGPL-3.0. The
          SDK and CLI are MIT. You may self-host, modify, and redistribute
          the code under the applicable license. See COMMERCIAL.md in the
          GitHub repository for the dual-license details.
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- warranty disclaimer -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-[18px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-text">
          <span class="text-accent">├&nbsp;</span>
          warranty disclaimer
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-muted-strong">
          edgepush is provided &quot;as is&quot; without warranty of any kind.
          We do not warrant that the service will be uninterrupted, error-free,
          or secure. You use the service at your own risk.
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- limitation of liability -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-[18px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-text">
          <span class="text-accent">├&nbsp;</span>
          limitation of liability
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-muted-strong">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, edgepush and its authors
          shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or
          consequential damages arising from your use of the service. This
          includes but is not limited to lost messages, lost data, and lost
          revenue.
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- termination -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-[18px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-text">
          <span class="text-accent">├&nbsp;</span>
          termination
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-muted-strong">
          We may suspend or terminate your access at any time for any reason
          including, without limitation, abuse, spam, or violation of these
          terms.
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- changes -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-[18px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-text">
          <span class="text-accent">├&nbsp;</span>
          changes
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-muted-strong">
          We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the
          service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- contact -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-[18px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-text">
          <span class="text-accent">├&nbsp;</span>
          contact
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-sans text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-muted-strong">
          Questions? Email
          <a
            href="mailto:contact@edgepush.dev"
            class="text-text underline decoration-accent underline-offset-4 hover:text-accent"
          >contact@edgepush.dev</a>.
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</Base>
